I love this song so much, have already listened to over 30 times in a day. The production, the vocals, everything is just perfect, love Coke Studio for exploring different genres in Punjabi music this year.
I honestly relate to this song too much, I have been too confused about my life for previous 11 months since I graduated. Hadn't been able to move forward, just stayed put, finally I have decided to go with the flow of life, wherever it takes me, and I understood we can't be everything we wish to be, but life makes us many things which I think is make it worth living.
